sequenceDiagram
  participant ATT as Attendee Client
  participant WS as WebSocket Handler
  participant FAC as Facilitator Client
  participant DB as DB

  ATT->>WS: 1) step progress / help / chat
  WS->>DB: 2) persist event
  WS->>FAC: 3) broadcast status / DM
  FAC->>WS: 4) resolve help / DM
  WS->>ATT: 5) status update
  WS->>DB: 6) append chat/help history
